'''argot'''

#A secret language or conventional slang peculiar to thieves, tramps, and vagabonds.
#The specialized vocabulary and terminology used between people with special skill in a field, such as between doctors, mathematicians or [[hacker]]s.
#:''The conversation was in the '''argot''' of the trade, full of acronyms and abbreviations that made no sense to the [[uninitiate]].''


